# Multidimensional Parallax Protocol v1.0
## Purpose
Decompress perceived patterns using multiple cues across layered domains.
## Inputs
- Observed pattern (compressed representation)
## Cues
- spatial
- temporal
- causal
- incentive
- statistical
- comparative
- counterfactual
## Layers
- physical
- biological
- cognitive
- social
- symbolic
## Process
1. Apply multiple cues to the same pattern
2. Evaluate across multiple layers
3. Compare outputs
4. Identify invariants (stable relationships)
5. Discard non-stable projections
## Output
- higher-fidelity structure
- reduced illusion risk
- actionable insight
## Principle
Truth survives across independent cues and layered perspectives.

